{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Memperingati 20 Tahun Anniversary Harry Potter","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tepat 31 Juli lalu, penulis terkenal JK. Rowling baru aja merayakan ulang tahunnya yang ke 52 tahun. Ulang tahunnya bersamaan dengan ulang tahun karakter buatannya, Harry Potter yang sekarang udah berumur 37 tahun! Buku pertama dari series Harry Potter yang berjudul ‘<em>Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone</em>’ saat itu dirilis pada 26 Juni 1997, yang dimana diceritakan dalam bukunya, Harry baru berumur 11 tahun. Rowling bercerita kalau dia menghabiskan 5 tahun untuk mendesain dunia di buku pertama Harry Potter series. Sejak kecil, penulis ini memang suka banget dengan cerita fiksi bernuansa magis. Karena menurutnya, saat masih kecil, kita sulit untuk melakukan banyak hal karena <em>powerless. </em>Sementara cerita tentang dunia sihir dan magis yang hadir dalam buku cerita anak dapat membangun imajinasi yang menyenangkan, yaitu semuanya mungkin bisa dilakukan hanya dengan tongkat ajaib atau mantra sihir.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12624\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12624\" data-attachment-id=\"12624\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/3-106/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Happy birthday Harry! (Sumber: hypable.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Happy birthday Harry! (Sumber: hypable.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12624\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"Happy birthday Harry! (Sumber: hypable.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12624\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Happy birthday Harry! (Sumber: hypable.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12618\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12618\" data-attachment-id=\"12618\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/1-106/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"JK Rowling (Sumber: boomsbeat.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;JK Rowling (Sumber: boomsbeat.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12618\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-4.jpg\" alt=\"JK Rowling (Sumber: boomsbeat.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12618\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">JK Rowling (Sumber: boomsbeat.com)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">J.K. Rowling juga sering membalas pertanyaan fans tentang tokoh maupun cerita Harry Potter lewat akun twitternya loh! Berikut beberapa jawaban dari J. K. Rowling ketika membalas pertanyaan:</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12642\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12642\" data-attachment-id=\"12642\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/9-35/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: twitter.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12642\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12642\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: twitter.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Q: Selain Harry, siapa karakter favoritmu di dalam series?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A: Dumbledore.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12639\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12639\" data-attachment-id=\"12639\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/8-41/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: twitter.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12639\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12639\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: twitter.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Q: Apa Patronus dari Hagrids?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A: Hagrid gak bisa membuat Patronus karena sulit banget untuk mengejanya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12633\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12633\" data-attachment-id=\"12633\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/6-63/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: twitter.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12633\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: twitter.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12633\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: twitter.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Q: Kamu gak menerima surat (dari Hogwarts), kalau gitu kamu muggle (manusia) atau squib (anak yang lahir dari penyihir tapi gak memiliki kemampuan sihir). Apa kamu squib?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A: Untuk semua orang bilang kalau mereka gak pernah dapat surat dari Hogwarts: kalian udah dapat suratnya. Kalian juga udah pergi ke Hogwarts. Kita semua pernah disana bersama.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12636\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12636\" data-attachment-id=\"12636\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/7-49/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.lib-rary.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.lib-rary.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12636\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.lib-rary.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12636\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.lib-rary.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perayaan ulang tahun ke 20 dari buku Harry Potter (yang dirilis di tahun 1997 pertama kali), juga dirayakan juga oleh The Library, sebuah club pecinta buku di UK. The Library merilis menu makan malam bertemakan makanan yang ada di buku dan film Harry Potter seperti ButterBeer, menu minuman dan <em>Amuse Bouche </em>berbentuk surat kiriman dari Hogwarts yang terbuat dari rice paper bertuliskan tinta cumi. Sebelum makanan disajikan, ada pun ‘professor’ dari Hogwarts yang menjelaskan cerita di balik menu dan di buku ke-berapa makanan itu muncul di dalam film Harry Potter. Unik banget kan? Ditambah lagi, semua yang datang disarankan untuk memakai kostum supaya makin <em>immersed </em>ke dalam dunia para penyihir.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12621\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12621\" data-attachment-id=\"12621\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/memperingati-20-tahun-anniversary-harry-potter/attachment/2-79/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.bl.uk\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.bl.uk&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12621\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.bl.uk\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12621\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.bl.uk</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Buat kamu yang suka dengan cerita Harry Potter dan masih belum bisa <em>move on</em> dari seriesnya, ada <em>good news</em>! Bloomsbury Publishing akan menerbitkan buku berjudul ‘Harry Potter: A History of Magic’ di bulan Oktober nanti. Buku ini akan berisi mata pelajaran yang diajarkan dalam Hogwarts, seperti Herbology atau ramuan-ramuan magis dan Perawatan untuk Makhluk Sihir. Di buku itu nantinya juga akan menampilkan sketsa dan manuscript Harry Potter dari J. K. Rowling dalam pembuatan filmnya. Udah gak sabar kan pasti untuk baca bukunya?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"f37439f6-7ab8-5832-8366-bf7651cdf85e"}}}